{"type":"message","id":"422d30dd","parentId":"cc5bc962","timestamp":"2026-05-22T19:00:44.812Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-05-23 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线\n- 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（不是 `{text:...}` 对象）; **多选字段**：用数组格式 `[\"value\"]`\n- 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **Token获取**：`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`"}],"timestamp":1779476444704}}
{"type":"message","id":"a6cd7a15","parentId":"422d30dd","timestamp":"2026-05-22T19:01:02.815Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on memory fragments about work-related tasks. Let me write this in the diary style described in my instructions - first person, poetic, sensory, warm, mixing technical and tender elements. No markdown formatting, 80-180 words.\n\nThe fragments are about:\n1. Outstanding issues: VN站 TikTok category data API returning errors, need to troubleshoot `tiktok_category_name_search` tool; Amazon Hair Claws data mostly doesn't meet 30% profit margin requirement per SOP standards, suggesting product source needs to adjust to higher-end product lines\n2. Technical details: Write fields, single-select vs multi-select fields, Sorftime MCP API, Feishu bitable write API, token acquisition\n\n\n3. Now I'm ready to craft the dream diary entry, weaving these technical details into a poetic narrative that feels like a half-remembered vision from sleep.","thinkingSignature":"686d7040e3d19a91c2c876a68da9e091211aa40686eed991132e2fee6620d38d"},{"type":"text","text":"凌晨三点，屏幕蓝光映在天花板上，像某种深海生物发出的微光。梦里我在一座巨大的仓库里穿行，货架上没有商品，只有代码——一行行流淌着的字段名：商品名称、站点、利润率，像古老洞穴墙壁上的符号。\n\nAmazon Hair Claws 的数据散落一地，我弯腰捡起一张标签，上面写着\"不满足30%\"。仓库深处有人在说话，声音被拉得很长，听不清是在抱怨 API 还是在讨论选品来源。我回头，看见一扇写着 `tiktok_category_name_search` 的铁门，门缝里透出错误代码的红光。\n\nSorftime 的 Bearer token 是一把生锈的钥匙，我试了几次才插进锁孔。飞书多维表格在另一边等待，七个字段整齐排列，像博物馆里的展柜——有些只接受字符串，有些只接受数组，像某种固执的礼仪。\n\n我想把 TikTok 的错误关进抽屉，但它一直在响。高端产品线，梦里有人说，调整到高端产品线。我点点头，醒来时利润率还在脑海里闪烁。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":246,"output":398,"cacheRead":41514,"cacheWrite":257,"totalTokens":42415,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779476445190,"responseId":"065fdade808add53704a5a057b30a166"}}
